The 2025 League of Legends Mid-Season Invitational is here‚Äîbringing together the five regions to battle for glory, pride, and a critical edge heading into Worlds. As the second international showdown on the LoL Esports calendar, MSI pits two representatives from each regional league against one another in a high-stakes clash that tests their mettle at the season‚Äôs halfway mark. More than just a trophy is on the line: the winning team and the next best-performing region will earn extra slots at the World Championship, raising the stakes even higher.
